{"tid":921217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓三警察借口「掃毒」砌生豬肉及謀殺中學生罪成","createTime":"2018-11-29T11:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T12:28:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"15117d68adf166e12725096b02d8c873f5c25a65","tid":921217,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=328992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328992&d=LOWRjEZdlJ9taF7QOdS7BBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=535ae043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328992&h=02bb2fad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=328992</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】菲律賓三名警察被裁定謀殺一名中學生罪成，是總統杜特爾特發動「掃毒戰」以來，首次有警察因濫殺被定罪。<br />\n<br />\n案件在菲律賓第三大城市卡洛奧坎的地方法院審理，判決後三名被告被押解離開。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判決書指出，先開槍後思索這種態度在文明社會絕不能接受，殺人從來不是執法者的職責，他裁定三名警察謀殺罪成，判監最多40年，並要賠款給死者家屬。<br />\n<br />\n案中死者是17歲中學生桑托斯，居於馬尼拉北部市郊。閉路電視拍攝到去年8月，他被警察強行拖走，最後死在一條小巷。警察指他替毒販運送毒品，聲稱案發時桑托斯持槍反抗，因此出於自衛殺人，但有目擊者指桑托斯根本沒有手持武器，是警察栽贓。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特發動「掃毒戰」近兩年半以來，菲律賓有近五千人死於警方行動中，被人權組織批評濫殺。"},{"pid":"c3ddd56b0c0041426068119ab403daeccc1c1f88","tid":921217,"uid":582,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"死火，child登仔好buy呢個菲律賓侵侵架喎"},{"pid":"c7135ef146cc85f225dda9297256faa296ee18fb","tid":921217,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15117d68adf166e12725096b02d8c873f5c25a65","tid":921217,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=328992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328992&d=LOWRjEZdlJ9taF7QOdS7BBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=535ae043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.l